name: Astrobros Mission #3: Pera
description: What up crew! We’re stoked to have you along for our 3rd mission! My name is Pascal, but you know me as the Green Astrobro. I’m doin the log today so come and follow along!  Pascals’ Log: We landed on Pera today. So fricken pretty! I couldn’t look away from the scenery! Until of course Quinn! Had to get his frisbee stuck on a big ass leaf! I’m not usually one to get frustrated but oooh man, we told him not to bring it. “BuT HeAdQuaRtErS SaId He CoUlD” anyway we’re trying to get it out no-...wait who is that…? *Signal Lost*
